comments: Azubuike (UTA) moves laterally into Davis' (LAL) body and delivers contact during the layup attempt.
Olynyk (UTA) brings both hands toward Russell's (LAL) body and marginal contact occurs as he releases away to roll.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in Dunn's (UTA) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Davis (LAL) is already established in Dunn's (UTA) path and absorbs the contact as they come together in the lane.
Azubuike (UTA) initiates the contact by facing Davis (LAL) up and impeding him during the rebound.
Azubuike (UTA) and Davis (LAL) mutually come together off-ball and marginal contact occurs as they engage for position.
Hachimura (LAL) extends his arm and makes clean contact with the ball to dislodge it away from Dunn (UTA) at the end of the drive.
Hachimura (LAL) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.

Hachimura (LAL) does not maintain a legal vertical position when arm contact occurs with Olynyk (UTA) during his rip-through. The contact occurs during the rip-through and prior to Olynyk's upward shooting motion.
